11
00:00:28,083 --> 00:00:29,182
All I'm going to do is

12
00:00:29,183 --> 00:00:33,382
have Ms. Nakanishi show me around here and there.

13
00:00:33,383 --> 00:00:34,683
Really?

14
00:00:38,183 --> 00:00:39,282
What?

15
00:00:39,283 --> 00:00:40,882
Give that back to me, brat!

16
00:00:40,883 --> 00:00:42,882
How dare you steal it?

17
00:00:42,883 --> 00:00:44,682
I found it on the ground.

18
00:00:44,683 --> 00:00:46,682
What's this passionate conversation about?

19
00:00:46,683 --> 00:00:48,182
A heart mark's written at the end, too.

20
00:00:48,183 --> 00:00:51,182
Well... That's... You see...

21
00:00:51,183 --> 00:00:52,683
That's hilarious.

22
00:00:53,683 --> 00:00:56,883
I'm glad you seem to have gotten over it already.

23
00:00:57,683 --> 00:00:59,582
