26
00:01:03,083 --> 00:01:04,582
It's a first.

27
00:01:04,583 --> 00:01:06,982
I mean... Idiot!

28
00:01:06,983 --> 00:01:08,582
Pops, the light's green!

29
00:01:08,583 --> 00:01:10,083
Right!

30
00:01:13,083 --> 00:01:15,082
A canvas stained black with crime.

31
00:01:15,083 --> 00:01:17,582
Vivid brilliant deduction skills change its color!

32
00:01:17,583 --> 00:01:19,782
I'm the third wheel on a three people drive.

33
00:01:19,783 --> 00:01:22,082
Where will the cheerful conversation lead to?

34
00:01:22,083 --> 00:01:23,682
He sees through the one and only truth.

35
00:01:23,683 --> 00:01:25,682
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

36
00:01:25,683 --> 00:01:27,883
His name is Detective Conan!

37
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:12,820
"Turning Point On A Driving Date"

38
00:03:14,038 --> 00:03:16,837
If I remember correctly, I think it was six months ago, right?

39
00:03:16,838 --> 00:03:19,937
Yeah. When I went to Haido Kitacho for work,

40
00:03:19,938 --> 00:03:21,738
I coincidentally ran into her.

41
00:03:22,938 --> 00:03:25,537
A woman named Remi Kirisaki was found hanging

42
00:03:25,538 --> 00:03:29,337
"Remi Kirisaki (30)" -in her room at her apartment.

43
00:03:29,338 --> 00:03:32,537
"Kiyomi Fukurai (58)" -She moved here three months ago,

44
00:03:32,538 --> 00:03:35,837
but since then she's been saying that she wanted to die,

45
00:03:35,838 --> 00:03:38,637
over and over.

46
00:03:38,638 --> 00:03:41,737
I used to live next to her and she always say that to me, too.

47
00:03:41,738 --> 00:03:45,337
Through the landlady and Ms. Kei Nakanishi's testimonies,

48
00:03:45,338 --> 00:03:47,137
as well as the suicide note that was found,

49
00:03:47,138 --> 00:03:49,637
it was apparent she had committed suicide.

50
00:03:49,638 --> 00:03:51,037
And on top of that,

51
00:03:51,038 --> 00:03:52,337
her handwriting on the rental agreement

52
00:03:52,338 --> 00:03:54,637
matched the writing of the suicide note.

53
00:03:54,638 --> 00:03:58,538
Kei blames herself for the death of her neighbor.

54
00:03:59,438 --> 00:04:01,137
It's my fault.

55
00:04:01,138 --> 00:04:05,137
Because I couldn't convince her to not commit suicide.

56
00:04:05,138 --> 00:04:07,737
Stop blaming yourself.

57
00:04:07,738 --> 00:04:08,937
But...

58
00:04:08,938 --> 00:04:12,437
She's the one who made the final decision to commit suicide.

59
00:04:12,438 --> 00:04:14,438
You're not responsible.

60
00:04:16,138 --> 00:04:20,137
You don't know how much what you said meant to me.

61
00:04:20,138 --> 00:04:22,338
That's why I sent you the thank you letter.

62
00:04:23,438 --> 00:04:24,937
I'm currently in my hometown

63
00:04:24,938 --> 00:04:28,437
