253
00:14:24,077 --> 00:14:27,876
I disguised myself by using a fake mustache.

254
00:14:27,877 --> 00:14:29,177
That's nothing to boast about!

255
00:14:32,377 --> 00:14:33,976
Well built...

256
00:14:33,977 --> 00:14:35,676
No matter how well you disguise yourself,

257
00:14:35,677 --> 00:14:38,376
you can't do anything about the physique, can you?

258
00:14:38,377 --> 00:14:40,276
I guess not.

259
00:14:40,277 --> 00:14:42,177
What?

260
00:14:43,577 --> 00:14:46,276
Let's go to Shikabanezaki, the goal, the sea coast!

261
00:14:46,277 --> 00:14:47,477
Okay.

262
00:14:55,777 --> 00:14:58,476
It's so beautiful and refreshing.

263
00:14:58,477 --> 00:14:59,976
Yes.

